title: american horror story : coven - Axeman Massacre witch hunters
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: I just adore Marie taking pictures without a care in the world.
I know they were both completely crazy and toxic for eachother, but “I love you more than jazz, babydoll” had me swooning 🥺😩
Sooo...the head of the witch hunters business weren't prepared for a supernatural attack...?

My favourite part of the scene is the look on Marie's face when Fiona sinks that axe into the fox's neck... Maybe she always thought of the coven witches as people who weren't willing to get their hands dirty, but did she ever.
LOL Marie just casually looks at her phone after a bloody massacre.
